description: This file is the main entry point for a React application. It imports React, ReactDOM, styles, and the main App component. It initializes the React application by rendering the App component inside the DOM element with id 'root'.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a React root for rendering the application inside a DOM element.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React element into the root DOM node.
